@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Default Toolbar";
    ViewData["DemoNumber"] = 6;
}
<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-2xl px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[260px_1fr]">
        <partial name="Demos/_DemoLayout" />
        <div>
            <div class="demo-card">
                <div class="demo-card-header">Default Toolbar</div>
                <div class="demo-card-body">
                    <p class="demo-description">The default toolbar provides the most commonly used formatting options in a clean, organized layout. It strikes a balance between functionality and simplicity, making it the best choice for most content editing scenarios.</p>

                    <richtextbox
                        id="defaultToolbarEditor"
                        name="defaultToolbarEditor"
                        toolbar="{bold,italic,underline,forecolor,backcolor}|{justifyleft,justifycenter,justifyright}|{insertorderedlist,insertunorderedlist,indent,outdent} #{paragraphs:toggle,fontname:toggle,fontsize:toggle}|{undo,redo} / {insertlink,unlink}|{inserttable,insertimage,insertgallery}|{insertblockquote,insertemoji,insertchars,inserttemplate} #{removeformat,code,toggleborder,fullscreenenter,togglemore}"
                        skin="default"
                        width="100%"
                        height="350px"
                        html="<h3>Meeting Notes - Product Review</h3><p><strong>Date:</strong> Monday, April 7 | <strong>Duration:</strong> 45 minutes</p><p><strong>Attendees:</strong></p><ul><li>Sarah Chen - Product Manager</li><li>Marcus Johnson - Lead Engineer</li><li>Priya Patel - UX Designer</li><li>David Kim - QA Lead</li></ul><h3>Action Items</h3><ul><li>Sarah: Share updated wireframes with the team by Wednesday</li><li>Marcus: Set up staging environment for beta testing</li><li>Priya: Conduct usability testing with five participants</li><li>David: Prepare regression test suite for the new release</li></ul><p>Overall the sprint is progressing well. The team agreed to hold a follow-up session on Thursday to review the updated designs before moving into development. No blockers were identified.</p>"></richtextbox>

                    <div class="demo-note">
                        <div class="demo-note-content">
                            <div class="demo-note-title">Note</div>
                            <p class="demo-note-text">The default preset balances functionality and simplicity. It includes text formatting, lists, links, and image insertion.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="code-panel">
                        <pre><code>&lt;richtextbox
    name="defaultToolbarEditor"
    toolbar="{bold,italic,underline,forecolor,backcolor}
             |{justifyleft,justifycenter,justifyright,justifyfull}
             |{insertorderedlist,insertunorderedlist,indent,outdent}
             |{insertblockquote,insertemoji}
             #{paragraphs:toggle,fontname:toggle,fontsize:toggle,lineheight}
             |{undo,redo}
             / {formatpainter,removeformat}|{insertlink,unlink}
             |{inserttable,insertimage,insertgallery,insertvideo,
               insertdocument,inserttemplate}|{insertchars,insertcode}
             #{preview,code,selectall}
             |{toggleborder,fullscreenenter,fullscreenexit,togglemore}"
    skin="default"
    height="350px" /&gt;</code></pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
